# The gitignored subrepos. ANCHOR THESE (`/name/`, not `name`): an unanchored
# name matches a directory at ANY depth, so a bare `tempest` also swallowed
# reference/atari-source/tempest/ — 57 files of vendored ROM source vanished from
# `git add` without a word. Only the top-level checkout is the subrepo.
/tempest/
/lobby/
/star-wars/
/asteroids/
/battlezone/
/red-baron/
/centipede/
/joust/
/arcade-shared/
out/audio/
